<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN231">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>eṟipuṉak kuṟavaṉ kuṟaiya laṉṉa</l>
<l>karipuṟa viṟaki ṉīma moḷḷaḻaṟ</l>
<l>kuṟukiṉuṅ kuṟukuka kuṟukātu ceṉṟu</l>
<l>vicumpuṟa nīḷiṉu nīḷka pacuṅkatirt</l>
<l>tiṅka ḷaṉṉa veṇkuṭai</l>
<l>yoṇñāyi ṟaṉṉōṉ pukaḻmā yalavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The bright fire of the funeral pyre with firewood charred outside,</l>
<l>like the plots of the hill people whose fields [are cleared] by flame,</l>
<l>if it comes near [him], let it come near. If it does not come near, goes</l>
<l>[and] extends so as to reach the sky, let it extend. </l>
<l>The [words of] praise for him who was like the bright sun,</l>
<l>[his] white umbrella like the fresh-rayed moon,</l>
<l>	will not vanish.</l>
</lg>
